How was she still standing?

270
00:40:05.000 --> 00:40:06.700
Bitch isn't standing now.

271
00:40:11.500 --> 00:40:15.100
- What was all the shooting?
- We found a survivor.

272
00:40:15.600 --> 00:40:19.500
